item.title: Clothes Donation
item.description: Summer Clothes Donation For Underprivileged Kids Summer clothes starting from the age group of 3 years. We are going to donate mainly to kids at the underprivileged schools. My request to Plz donate only those which can be useful for the kids. Also footwear can of use for them.
